<title>mlʾ ạlḥb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 bmlʾ ạlḥb wạlạ̹tḍạʿ rby rḍyt bạlṣlyb
 ạ̉kẖlyt dẖạtk dẖqt ạlạ̉wjạʿ lạ̉jly yạ ạ̉gẖly̱ ḥbyb
 fạ̉y ḥb ysẖbh ḥbk ạ̉ʿtqtny mn kl qyd
 mlktny mlktny dʿwtny lʿhd jdyd
 mn fyḍ ḥbk ạ̉ḍrm fw̉ạdy fḥb rby sr ạlḥyạẗ
 sẖms ạldhwr dẖlạaⁿ qblt mlk ạlmlwk ʿạrạaⁿ ḥmlt
 gẖfrt ly fwq ạlṣlyb gẖmrtny bḥb ʿjyb
 fkyf tsẖfy rgẖm ạlậlậm wyfyḍ mn ʿynyk nbʿ ḥnạn
 ạ̉dẖkrny rby fy mlkk ạstwdʿ rwḥy fy ḥḍnk
 ạ̉hdyk qlby kly wmạ ly yạ sydy rb ạlḥyạẗ</lyrics>
